Package: visPedigree
Type: Package
Title: Tidying and Visualizing Animal Pedigrees
Version: 0.6.2
Authors@R: person("Sheng","Luan", email="luansheng@foxmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of tools for tidying, pruning, and 
    visualizing animal pedigrees. Leveraging the 'data.table' package for 
    high-performance data manipulation and 'igraph' for sophisticated 
    hierarchical layouts, it supports S3 classes for seamless integration 
    into R workflows. Key features include pedigree validation, loop 
    detection, ancestry tracing (upward, downward, or both), and the 
    generation of legible vector-based PDF graphs. A unique compaction 
    algorithm allows for the visualization of extremely large pedigrees 
    (e.g., nucleus breeding populations in aquaculture) by grouping 
    full-sib families without losing structural information.
